    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Trying your recipe as we speak. Getting popover tins in Sweden is impossible, so it&#39;s been a bit hit and miss with the muffin tins, but I never give up. I like to add a tsp or so of dijon to give them a savory flavor. We have them with dinner most often. My question is though does anyone know how The Cliff House in SF make their popovers? Been searching and searching for their recipe.</p>
    </div>

